{"slug":"point-value","category":"life","subcategory":"shopping","title":"ポイント還元計算","description":"ポイント還元率から実質割引額・年間お得額を計算。","metaTitle":"ポイント還元率計算ツール｜実質割引額を自動計算","metaDescription":"ポイント還元率と利用金額から実質的な割引額を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"pointValue","inputs":[{"id":"amount","label":"利用金額","type":"number","unit":"円","default":10000,"min":0,"max":99999999,"step":100},{"id":"rate","label":"還元率","type":"number","unit":"%","default":1,"min":0,"max":50,"step":0.1},{"id":"monthlySpend","label":"月間平均利用額","type":"number","unit":"円","default":100000,"min":0,"max":10000000,"step":1000}],"outputs":[{"id":"pointsEarned","label":"獲得ポイント","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"discountEquivalent","label":"実質割引額","format":"currency"},{"id":"annualSavings","label":"年間お得額","format":"currency"}],"explanation":"<h3>還元率の比較</h3><p>一般カード0.5〜1%、高還元カード1.5〜2%程度です。</p>","faq":[{"question":"1%と2%の差は？","answer":"月10万円利用なら年間12,000円の差です。"},{"question":"有効期限は？","answer":"カード会社により1年〜無期限まで様々です。"}],"related":["discount","tax-included"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"electricity-cost","category":"life","subcategory":"shopping","title":"電気代計算","description":"家電の消費電力と使用時間から電気代を計算。","metaTitle":"電気代計算ツール｜家電の電気代を自動計算","metaDescription":"消費電力と使用時間を入力して1日・1ヶ月・1年の電気代を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"electricityCost","inputs":[{"id":"watt","label":"消費電力","type":"number","unit":"W","default":1000,"min":0,"max":100000,"step":1},{"id":"hoursPerDay","label":"1日の使用時間","type":"number","unit":"時間","default":8,"min":0,"max":24,"step":0.5},{"id":"pricePerKwh","label":"電気料金単価","type":"number","unit":"円/kWh","default":35,"min":10,"max":100,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"dailyCost","label":"1日の電気代","format":"currency"},{"id":"monthlyCost","label":"1ヶ月の電気代","format":"currency","primary":True},{"id":"annualCost","label":"1年間の電気代","format":"currency"},{"id":"kwhPerMonth","label":"月間消費電力量","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>電気代の計算式</h3><p>電気代 = 消費電力(W) ÷ 1000 × 使用時間(h) × 電気料金単価(円/kWh)</p>","faq":[{"question":"電気料金の単価は？","answer":"約30〜40円/kWhが目安です。"},{"question":"待機電力はどのくらい？","answer":"一般家庭で年間約6,000〜8,000円です。"}],"related":["discount","per-unit-price"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"tip-calculator","category":"life","subcategory":"shopping","title":"チップ計算","description":"食事代からチップ額と合計金額を計算。","metaTitle":"チップ計算ツール｜食事代からチップ額を自動計算","metaDescription":"食事代とチップ率を入力してチップ額と合計金額を自動計算。割り勘対応。","calculatorFunction":"tipCalculator","inputs":[{"id":"billAmount","label":"食事代","type":"number","unit":"ドル","default":50,"min":0,"max":100000,"step":1},{"id":"tipRate","label":"チップ率","type":"number","unit":"%","default":18,"min":0,"max":50,"step":1},{"id":"people","label":"人数","type":"number","unit":"人","default":2,"min":1,"max":20,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"tipAmount","label":"チップ額","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"totalBill","label":"合計金額","format":"number"},{"id":"perPerson","label":"1人あたり","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>チップの相場</h3><p>アメリカ: 15〜20%、ヨーロッパ: 5〜10%。日本にはチップ文化はありません。</p>","faq":[{"question":"チップはいつ払う？","answer":"レストランでは会計時にクレジットカード伝票に記入するか、現金をテーブルに置きます。"},{"question":"不要な国は？","answer":"日本、韓国、中国、オーストラリアなどでは不要です。"}],"related":["split-bill","discount"],"popular":False},

# ===== life/car =====
{"slug":"car-cost","category":"life","subcategory":"car","title":"車の維持費計算","description":"車種別の年間維持費（税金・保険・車検・ガソリン）を総合計算。","metaTitle":"車の維持費計算ツール｜年間コストを項目別に自動計算","metaDescription":"車種を選ぶだけで年間の維持費を項目別に自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"carCostTotal","inputs":[{"id":"carType","label":"車種","type":"select","options":[{"value":"kei","label":"軽自動車"},{"value":"compact","label":"コンパクトカー"},{"value":"sedan","label":"セダン"},{"value":"suv","label":"SUV"},{"value":"minivan","label":"ミニバン"}],"default":"compact"},{"id":"annualMileage","label":"年間走行距離","type":"number","unit":"km","default":10000,"min":0,"max":100000,"step":1000},{"id":"fuelEfficiency","label":"燃費","type":"number","unit":"km/L","default":15,"min":1,"max":50,"step":0.5},{"id":"fuelPrice","label":"ガソリン単価","type":"number","unit":"円/L","default":175,"min":100,"max":300,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"taxCost","label":"自動車税","format":"currency"},{"id":"insuranceCost","label":"任意保険（年額概算）","format":"currency"},{"id":"inspectionCost","label":"車検費用（年割り）","format":"currency"},{"id":"fuelCostTotal","label":"ガソリン代","format":"currency"},{"id":"totalAnnualCost","label":"年間維持費合計","format":"currency","primary":True},{"id":"monthlyCost","label":"月額換算","format":"currency"}],"explanation":"<h3>車の維持費の内訳</h3><p>自動車税、任意保険、車検、ガソリン代が主な項目です。軽自動車は普通車より年間10〜20万円安くなります。</p>","faq":[{"question":"年間いくら？","answer":"軽自動車で約30〜40万円、コンパクトカーで約40〜50万円が目安です。"},{"question":"カーシェアと自家用車どちらが得？","answer":"月300km以下ならカーシェアが安い場合が多いです。"}],"related":["fuel-cost","car-tax","car-insurance"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"ev-cost","category":"life","subcategory":"car","title":"EV vs ガソリン車コスト比較","description":"電気自動車とガソリン車の燃料費・維持費を比較計算。","metaTitle":"EV vs ガソリン車コスト比較ツール｜総コストを自動シミュレーション","metaDescription":"EVとガソリン車の燃料費を比較。何年で元が取れるか自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"evCostComparison","inputs":[{"id":"annualMileage","label":"年間走行距離","type":"number","unit":"km","default":10000,"min":0,"max":100000,"step":1000},{"id":"evEfficiency","label":"EV電費","type":"number","unit":"km/kWh","default":6,"min":2,"max":10,"step":0.1},{"id":"electricityPrice","label":"電気料金","type":"number","unit":"円/kWh","default":35,"min":10,"max":100,"step":1},{"id":"gasEfficiency","label":"ガソリン車燃費","type":"number","unit":"km/L","default":15,"min":5,"max":40,"step":0.5},{"id":"gasPrice","label":"ガソリン単価","type":"number","unit":"円/L","default":175,"min":100,"max":300,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"evFuelCost","label":"EV年間電気代","format":"currency"},{"id":"gasFuelCost","label":"ガソリン年間燃料代","format":"currency"},{"id":"annualSavings","label":"年間燃料費の差額","format":"currency","primary":True},{"id":"tenYearSavings","label":"10年間の燃料費差額","format":"currency"}],"explanation":"<h3>EVの燃料費メリット</h3><p>EVは1km約5.8円、ガソリン車は1km約11.7円。燃料費は約半分です。</p>","faq":[{"question":"EVの方が安い？","answer":"燃料費は安いですが車両価格が高いため、走行距離次第です。"},{"question":"充電はどこで？","answer":"自宅充電が基本。外出先は急速充電スタンドを利用します。"}],"related":["fuel-cost","car-cost"],"popular":False},

# ===== health/body =====
{"slug":"waist-hip-ratio","category":"health","subcategory":"body","title":"ウエスト・ヒップ比計算","description":"ウエストとヒップの比率からメタボリスクを判定。","metaTitle":"ウエスト・ヒップ比計算ツール｜メタボリスクを自動判定","metaDescription":"ウエストとヒップを入力してWHRとメタボリスクを自動判定。","calculatorFunction":"waistHipRatio","inputs":[{"id":"waist","label":"ウエスト","type":"number","unit":"cm","default":80,"min":40,"max":200,"step":0.1},{"id":"hip","label":"ヒップ","type":"number","unit":"cm","default":95,"min":40,"max":200,"step":0.1},{"id":"gender","label":"性別","type":"select","options":[{"value":"male","label":"男性"},{"value":"female","label":"女性"}],"default":"male"}],"outputs":[{"id":"whr","label":"ウエスト・ヒップ比","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"risk","label":"健康リスク","format":"text"},{"id":"bodyType","label":"体型タイプ","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>WHR</h3><p>男性0.90以上、女性0.85以上は内臓脂肪型肥満のリスク高です。</p>","faq":[{"question":"BMIとWHRどちらが重要？","answer":"WHRの方が心血管疾患リスク予測に優れるという研究もあります。"},{"question":"ウエストの測り方は？","answer":"おへその高さで息を吐いたときに測ります。"}],"related":["bmi","body-fat","ideal-weight"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"target-heart-rate","category":"health","subcategory":"body","title":"目標心拍数計算","description":"年齢と安静時心拍数から運動時の目標心拍数を計算。","metaTitle":"目標心拍数計算ツール｜運動強度別の心拍数を自動計算","metaDescription":"年齢と安静時心拍数を入力して運動強度別の目標心拍数を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"targetHeartRate","inputs":[{"id":"age","label":"年齢","type":"number","unit":"歳","default":35,"min":10,"max":100,"step":1},{"id":"restingHR","label":"安静時心拍数","type":"number","unit":"bpm","default":70,"min":30,"max":120,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"maxHR","label":"最大心拍数","format":"number"},{"id":"fatBurnZone","label":"脂肪燃焼ゾーン（50-60%）","format":"text","primary":True},{"id":"cardioZone","label":"有酸素ゾーン（60-70%）","format":"text"},{"id":"highIntensity","label":"高強度ゾーン（70-85%）","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>カルボーネン法</h3><p>目標心拍数 = （最大心拍数 - 安静時心拍数）× 運動強度(%) + 安静時心拍数</p>","faq":[{"question":"脂肪燃焼に最適な心拍数は？","answer":"最大心拍数の50〜60%です。35歳なら約120〜135bpm。"},{"question":"安静時心拍数の測り方は？","answer":"朝起きてすぐ、座った状態で1分間の脈拍を数えます。"}],"related":["calorie-burn","basal-metabolism"],"popular":False},

# ===== health/calorie =====
{"slug":"meal-calorie","category":"health","subcategory":"calorie","title":"食事カロリー計算","description":"主要食品のカロリーを合計計算。","metaTitle":"食事カロリー計算ツール｜1食分のカロリーを自動合計","metaDescription":"主要食品の量を入力して1食分のカロリーを自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"mealCalorie","inputs":[{"id":"rice","label":"ご飯","type":"number","unit":"g","default":150,"min":0,"max":1000,"step":10},{"id":"meat","label":"肉類","type":"number","unit":"g","default":100,"min":0,"max":1000,"step":10},{"id":"fish","label":"魚介類","type":"number","unit":"g","default":0,"min":0,"max":1000,"step":10},{"id":"vegetables","label":"野菜類","type":"number","unit":"g","default":100,"min":0,"max":1000,"step":10},{"id":"oil","label":"油脂類","type":"number","unit":"g","default":10,"min":0,"max":100,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"totalCalorie","label":"合計カロリー","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"protein","label":"タンパク質（概算）","format":"number"},{"id":"fat","label":"脂質（概算）","format":"number"},{"id":"carbs","label":"炭水化物（概算）","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>100gあたりのカロリー目安</h3><p>白米: 168kcal、鶏むね肉: 108kcal、豚バラ: 386kcal、野菜: 20〜30kcal、油: 921kcal</p>","faq":[{"question":"1日の適正カロリーは？","answer":"成人男性2,200〜2,600kcal、成人女性1,800〜2,200kcal程度です。"},{"question":"月1kg痩せるには？","answer":"1日約240kcal減らす計算です（7,200kcal÷30日）。"}],"related":["daily-calorie","calorie-burn"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"alcohol-calorie","category":"health","subcategory":"calorie","title":"お酒のカロリー計算","description":"飲酒量からカロリーと純アルコール量を計算。","metaTitle":"お酒のカロリー計算ツール｜飲酒量からカロリーを自動計算","metaDescription":"ビール・日本酒・ワインの飲酒量からカロリーとアルコール量を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"alcoholCalorie","inputs":[{"id":"drinkType","label":"お酒の種類","type":"select","options":[{"value":"beer","label":"ビール（5%）"},{"value":"sake","label":"日本酒（15%）"},{"value":"wine","label":"ワイン（12%）"},{"value":"whisky","label":"ウイスキー（40%）"},{"value":"shochu","label":"焼酎（25%）"},{"value":"chuhai","label":"チューハイ（5%）"}],"default":"beer"},{"id":"amount","label":"飲酒量","type":"number","unit":"ml","default":500,"min":0,"max":5000,"step":50}],"outputs":[{"id":"calories","label":"カロリー","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"pureAlcohol","label":"純アルコール量","format":"number"},{"id":"drinkUnit","label":"ドリンク数","format":"number"},{"id":"decompositionTime","label":"分解時間（目安）","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>お酒のカロリー</h3><p>アルコール1gは7kcal。ビール500mlで約200kcal。</p>","faq":[{"question":"ビール500mlのカロリーは？","answer":"約200kcal。ご飯1杯分に近いです。"},{"question":"分解時間は？","answer":"体重60kgで純アルコール20gの分解に約3〜4時間です。"}],"related":["daily-calorie","meal-calorie"],"popular":False},

# ===== health/medical =====
{"slug":"medicine-dose","category":"health","subcategory":"medical","title":"薬の服用量計算","description":"体重から小児の薬の適正服用量を計算。","metaTitle":"薬の服用量計算ツール｜体重から適正量を自動計算","metaDescription":"体重と用量を入力して適正な服用量を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"medicineDose","inputs":[{"id":"weight","label":"体重","type":"number","unit":"kg","default":20,"min":1,"max":200,"step":0.1},{"id":"dosePerKg","label":"用量","type":"number","unit":"mg/kg","default":10,"min":0.1,"max":1000,"step":0.1},{"id":"timesPerDay","label":"服用回数","type":"number","unit":"回/日","default":3,"min":1,"max":6,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"singleDose","label":"1回の服用量","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"dailyDose","label":"1日の総量","format":"number"},{"id":"weeklyDose","label":"1週間の総量","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>注意</h3><p>本ツールは参考値です。実際の服用量は必ず医師・薬剤師の指示に従ってください。</p>","faq":[{"question":"子供の薬は大人の半分？","answer":"いいえ。必ず体重あたりの用量で計算してください。"},{"question":"体重が増えたら量も変わる？","answer":"はい。定期的に医師に確認しましょう。"}],"related":["medical-expense","high-cost-medical"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"blood-alcohol","category":"health","subcategory":"medical","title":"血中アルコール濃度計算","description":"飲酒量・体重から血中アルコール濃度と分解時間を計算。","metaTitle":"血中アルコール濃度計算ツール｜飲酒量から濃度と分解時間を自動計算","metaDescription":"飲酒量と体重を入力して血中アルコール濃度を自動計算。飲酒運転防止に。","calculatorFunction":"bloodAlcohol","inputs":[{"id":"weight","label":"体重","type":"number","unit":"kg","default":65,"min":30,"max":200,"step":1},{"id":"gender","label":"性別","type":"select","options":[{"value":"male","label":"男性"},{"value":"female","label":"女性"}],"default":"male"},{"id":"pureAlcohol","label":"純アルコール量","type":"number","unit":"g","default":20,"min":0,"max":200,"step":1},{"id":"hours","label":"経過時間","type":"number","unit":"時間","default":0,"min":0,"max":24,"step":0.5}],"outputs":[{"id":"bac","label":"血中アルコール濃度","format":"percent","primary":True},{"id":"soberTime","label":"完全分解時間","format":"number"},{"id":"status","label":"酔いの状態","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>飲酒運転の基準</h3><p>日本では血中0.03%以上で酒気帯び運転。0.05%以上で酒酔い運転です。</p>","faq":[{"question":"ビール1杯で運転できる？","answer":"ビール500mlの分解に3〜4時間。飲酒直後の運転は違法です。"},{"question":"寝れば覚める？","answer":"睡眠中も分解速度は変わりません。翌朝でも残っている可能性があります。"}],"related":["alcohol-calorie","medicine-dose"],"popular":False},

# ===== health/pregnancy =====
{"slug":"ovulation-day","category":"health","subcategory":"pregnancy","title":"排卵日予測計算","description":"生理周期から排卵日と妊娠しやすい時期を予測。","metaTitle":"排卵日予測計算ツール｜生理周期から排卵日を自動計算","metaDescription":"最終生理日と周期を入力して排卵日と妊娠しやすい期間を自動予測。","calculatorFunction":"ovulationDay","inputs":[{"id":"lastPeriod","label":"最終月経開始日","type":"date","default":"2026-03-01"},{"id":"cycleLength","label":"生理周期","type":"number","unit":"日","default":28,"min":21,"max":45,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"ovulationDate","label":"排卵予定日","format":"text","primary":True},{"id":"fertileStart","label":"妊娠しやすい期間（開始）","format":"text"},{"id":"fertileEnd","label":"妊娠しやすい期間（終了）","format":"text"},{"id":"nextPeriod","label":"次回生理予定日","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>排卵日の計算</h3><p>排卵は次の生理予定日の約14日前に起こります。</p>","faq":[{"question":"計算通りに排卵する？","answer":"個人差が大きいため、基礎体温や排卵検査薬の併用を推奨します。"},{"question":"周期が不規則な場合は？","answer":"計算精度が低下します。婦人科に相談しましょう。"}],"related":["due-date","pregnancy-week"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"baby-growth","category":"health","subcategory":"pregnancy","title":"赤ちゃん成長曲線計算","description":"月齢・体重・身長からパーセンタイル値を計算。","metaTitle":"赤ちゃん成長曲線計算ツール｜体重・身長のパーセンタイルを自動計算","metaDescription":"赤ちゃんの月齢・体重・身長を入力して成長の目安を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"babyGrowth","inputs":[{"id":"monthsAge","label":"月齢","type":"number","unit":"ヶ月","default":6,"min":0,"max":36,"step":1},{"id":"gender","label":"性別","type":"select","options":[{"value":"male","label":"男の子"},{"value":"female","label":"女の子"}],"default":"male"},{"id":"weight","label":"体重","type":"number","unit":"kg","default":7.5,"min":1,"max":25,"step":0.1},{"id":"height","label":"身長","type":"number","unit":"cm","default":67,"min":30,"max":120,"step":0.1}],"outputs":[{"id":"weightStatus","label":"体重の評価","format":"text","primary":True},{"id":"heightStatus","label":"身長の評価","format":"text"},{"id":"avgWeight","label":"同月齢の平均体重","format":"number"},{"id":"avgHeight","label":"同月齢の平均身長","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>成長曲線とは</h3><p>3〜97パーセンタイルの範囲内であれば正常な成長と考えられます。</p>","faq":[{"question":"曲線から外れていたら？","answer":"一時的なずれは問題ありません。成長のペースが一定かが重要です。"},{"question":"平均より重い/軽い","answer":"パーセンタイル範囲内なら問題ありません。"}],"related":["pregnancy-week","due-date"],"popular":False},

