{"slug":"gross-margin","category":"business","subcategory":"accounting","title":"粗利益率計算","description":"売上高と原価から粗利益・粗利益率を計算。","metaTitle":"粗利益率計算ツール｜売上高と原価から粗利益率を自動計算","metaDescription":"売上高と売上原価を入力して粗利益と粗利益率を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"grossMargin","inputs":[{"id":"revenue","label":"売上高","type":"number","unit":"万円","default":1000,"min":0,"max":10000000,"step":10},{"id":"cogs","label":"売上原価","type":"number","unit":"万円","default":600,"min":0,"max":10000000,"step":10}],"outputs":[{"id":"grossProfit","label":"粗利益","format":"currency"},{"id":"grossMarginRate","label":"粗利益率","format":"percent","primary":True},{"id":"markupRate","label":"原価率","format":"percent"}],"explanation":"<h3>粗利益率</h3><p>（売上高−原価）÷売上高×100。業種別目安: 小売25〜35%、飲食60〜70%、IT 70〜90%</p>","faq":[{"question":"粗利益と営業利益の違いは？","answer":"営業利益は粗利益からさらに販管費を引いたものです。"},{"question":"粗利益率を上げるには？","answer":"売価UP、原価DOWN、高粗利商品の比率UP。"}],"related":["profit-margin","break-even"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"working-capital","category":"business","subcategory":"accounting","title":"運転資金計算","description":"売掛金・買掛金・在庫から必要な運転資金を計算。","metaTitle":"運転資金計算ツール｜必要な運転資金を自動計算","metaDescription":"売掛金・買掛金・在庫を入力して必要な運転資金を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"workingCapital","inputs":[{"id":"receivables","label":"売掛金","type":"number","unit":"万円","default":500,"min":0,"max":10000000,"step":10},{"id":"inventory","label":"棚卸資産","type":"number","unit":"万円","default":300,"min":0,"max":10000000,"step":10},{"id":"payables","label":"買掛金","type":"number","unit":"万円","default":400,"min":0,"max":10000000,"step":10}],"outputs":[{"id":"workingCapital","label":"所要運転資金","format":"currency","primary":True},{"id":"turnoverDays","label":"運転資金回転日数","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>運転資金</h3><p>所要運転資金 = 売掛金 + 棚卸資産 − 買掛金</p>","faq":[{"question":"足りない場合は？","answer":"売掛金回収短縮、在庫削減、短期借入の活用が対策です。"},{"question":"黒字倒産とは？","answer":"利益は出ているが運転資金不足で支払いができなくなる状態です。"}],"related":["cash-flow","break-even"],"popular":False},

