{"slug":"hensachi","category":"education","subcategory":"school","title":"偏差値計算","description":"テストの点数から偏差値を計算。","metaTitle":"偏差値計算ツール｜テストの点数から偏差値を自動計算","metaDescription":"テストの点数と平均点を入力して偏差値を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"hensachi","inputs":[{"id":"score","label":"あなたの点数","type":"number","unit":"点","default":75,"min":0,"max":1000,"step":1},{"id":"average","label":"平均点","type":"number","unit":"点","default":60,"min":0,"max":1000,"step":1},{"id":"sd","label":"標準偏差","type":"number","unit":"","default":15,"min":0.1,"max":1000,"step":0.1}],"outputs":[{"id":"hensachi","label":"偏差値","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"percentile","label":"上位何%","format":"percent"},{"id":"rank","label":"100人中の順位","format":"number"}],"explanation":"<h3>偏差値の計算式</h3><p>偏差値 = (得点−平均点)÷標準偏差×10+50</p>","faq":[{"question":"100を超えることはある？","answer":"理論上はありますが実際にはほぼありません。"},{"question":"日本独自？","answer":"はい。海外ではパーセンタイル順位が一般的です。"}],"related":["exam-score","standard-deviation"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"scholarship","category":"education","subcategory":"school","title":"奨学金返済計算","description":"奨学金の総額・利率から月々の返済額を計算。","metaTitle":"奨学金返済計算シミュレーション｜月々の返済額を自動計算","metaDescription":"奨学金の借入総額と利率を入力して月々の返済額・返済総額を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"scholarship","inputs":[{"id":"totalBorrowed","label":"借入総額","type":"number","unit":"万円","default":300,"min":0,"max":10000,"step":10},{"id":"rate","label":"年利","type":"number","unit":"%","default":0.5,"min":0,"max":5,"step":0.01},{"id":"years","label":"返済期間","type":"number","unit":"年","default":15,"min":1,"max":20,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"monthlyPayment","label":"月々の返済額","format":"currency","primary":True},{"id":"totalPayment","label":"返済総額","format":"currency"},{"id":"totalInterest","label":"利息合計","format":"currency"}],"explanation":"<h3>JASSO奨学金</h3><p>第一種（無利子）と第二種（有利子、上限3%）があります。</p>","faq":[{"question":"返済開始はいつ？","answer":"卒業後7ヶ月目からです。"},{"question":"返済が厳しい場合は？","answer":"返済猶予（最長10年）、減額返還制度があります。"}],"related":["education-loan","debt-repayment"],"popular":False},

