{"slug":"typing-speed","category":"education","subcategory":"study","title":"タイピング速度計算","description":"入力文字数と時間からタイピング速度を計算。","metaTitle":"タイピング速度計算ツール｜WPM・CPMを自動計算","metaDescription":"入力文字数と所要時間からタイピング速度を自動計算。レベル判定付き。","calculatorFunction":"typingSpeed","inputs":[{"id":"characters","label":"入力文字数","type":"number","unit":"文字","default":300,"min":0,"max":100000,"step":1},{"id":"minutes","label":"所要時間","type":"number","unit":"分","default":5,"min":0.1,"max":120,"step":0.1}],"outputs":[{"id":"cpm","label":"CPM（文字/分）","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"wpm","label":"WPM（英単語/分）","format":"number"},{"id":"level","label":"レベル判定","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>速度の目安</h3><p>初心者: 〜100CPM、一般: 100〜200CPM、上級: 200〜400CPM</p>","faq":[{"question":"速いとどのくらい得？","answer":"1日2時間タイピングするなら速度2倍で年間240時間の差。"},{"question":"コツは？","answer":"ホームポジション、キーボードを見ない、正確性優先。"}],"related":["reading-speed","study-time"],"popular":False},
{"slug":"grade-calculator","category":"education","subcategory":"study","title":"成績計算","description":"各科目の得点から総合得点・平均点を計算。","metaTitle":"成績計算ツール｜科目別の得点から総合成績を自動計算","metaDescription":"各科目の得点を入力して総合得点・平均点を自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"gradeCalculator","inputs":[{"id":"subject1","label":"国語","type":"number","unit":"点","default":75,"min":0,"max":200,"step":1},{"id":"subject2","label":"数学","type":"number","unit":"点","default":80,"min":0,"max":200,"step":1},{"id":"subject3","label":"英語","type":"number","unit":"点","default":70,"min":0,"max":200,"step":1},{"id":"subject4","label":"理科","type":"number","unit":"点","default":85,"min":0,"max":200,"step":1},{"id":"subject5","label":"社会","type":"number","unit":"点","default":65,"min":0,"max":200,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"totalScore","label":"合計点","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"averageScore","label":"平均点","format":"number"},{"id":"highest","label":"最高点の科目","format":"text"},{"id":"lowest","label":"最低点の科目","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>5教科の合計</h3><p>各100点満点で500点満点。平均70点以上が上位校の目安。</p>","faq":[{"question":"内申点はどう計算？","answer":"5段階×9教科で45点満点。実技教科が2倍の自治体もあります。"},{"question":"合計点より偏差値？","answer":"はい。テスト難易度により変動するため偏差値が正確です。"}],"related":["exam-score","hensachi","gpa"],"popular":False},

