{"slug":"running-pace","category":"health","subcategory":"body","title":"ランニングペース計算","description":"距離と時間からペース（km/分）を計算。","metaTitle":"ランニングペース計算ツール｜距離と時間からペースを自動計算","metaDescription":"走った距離と時間を入力してペース（分/km）とスピードを自動計算。","calculatorFunction":"runningPace","inputs":[{"id":"distance","label":"距離","type":"number","unit":"km","default":5,"min":0.1,"max":200,"step":0.1},{"id":"hours","label":"時間","type":"number","unit":"時間","default":0,"min":0,"max":24,"step":1},{"id":"minutes","label":"分","type":"number","unit":"分","default":25,"min":0,"max":59,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"pace","label":"ペース（分/km）","format":"text","primary":True},{"id":"speed","label":"速度（km/h）","format":"number"},{"id":"marathon","label":"フルマラソン予想タイム","format":"text"},{"id":"half","label":"ハーフマラソン予想タイム","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>ランニングペースの目安</h3><p>初心者: 7〜8分/km、中級: 5〜6分/km、上級: 4分/km以下。マラソンサブ4は5分40秒/km。</p>","faq":[{"question":"サブ4とは？","answer":"フルマラソンを4時間以内で完走すること。ペースは5分40秒/km以内です。"},{"question":"5kmのタイム目安は？","answer":"初心者30〜40分、中級20〜25分、上級15〜20分。"}],"related":["calorie-burn","target-heart-rate"],"popular":False},

