{"slug":"photo-print","category":"life","subcategory":"unit","title":"写真プリントサイズ計算","description":"ピクセル数と解像度からプリント可能なサイズを計算。","metaTitle":"写真プリントサイズ計算ツール｜ピクセル数から印刷サイズを自動計算","metaDescription":"写真のピクセル数を入力して最大プリントサイズを自動計算。dpi解像度対応。","calculatorFunction":"photoPrint","inputs":[{"id":"widthPx","label":"横幅","type":"number","unit":"px","default":4000,"min":1,"max":100000,"step":1},{"id":"heightPx","label":"縦幅","type":"number","unit":"px","default":3000,"min":1,"max":100000,"step":1},{"id":"dpi","label":"解像度","type":"number","unit":"dpi","default":300,"min":72,"max":600,"step":1}],"outputs":[{"id":"widthCm","label":"横幅（cm）","format":"number","primary":True},{"id":"heightCm","label":"縦幅（cm）","format":"number"},{"id":"megapixels","label":"画素数","format":"number"},{"id":"aspectRatio","label":"アスペクト比","format":"text"}],"explanation":"<h3>印刷に必要な解像度</h3><p>一般的なプリント: 300dpi、大判ポスター: 150dpi、Web表示: 72dpi。</p>","faq":[{"question":"300dpiで十分？","answer":"一般的なプリント（A4まで）なら300dpiで十分な品質です。"},{"question":"スマホの写真はA4で印刷できる？","answer":"1200万画素以上（4000×3000px）ならA4 300dpiで十分な品質です。"}],"related":["data-size","area"],"popular":False},

